    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v1 = v1
    v2 = v2
    v1 = 0.89
    v2 = (((v2 + 0.79 + v2 + 0.45) * (tmp + 0.62 + v0 + 0.85)) - (v0 * tmp))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.exp(wp.cos(v0 + 0.75)))
    v0 = (wp.cos((v1 + 0.84 + v2 + 0.49)) - ((v1 + 0.88 / tmp + 0.95) / v2))
    v0 = 0.37
    data[tid] = v0
